武，略輸文采；唐宗宋祖，稍遜風騷。<br />\n 一代天驕，成吉思汗，只識彎弓射大雕。 <br />\n俱往矣，數風流人物，還看今朝！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"349ab8d5fb75c24c5a576fee00e17d7dc03b329d","tid":23364,"uid":46139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T01:52:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>老老豆豆 毛魔啲詩詞霸氣係噴晒出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n譬如？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n數天下英雄 還看今朝"},{"pid":"e297a502a511e9398ed9d2ae2ebee723637763e3","tid":23364,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T01:52:41.000Z","msg":"待到秋來九月八<br />\n<br />\n我花開後百花殺<br />\n<br />\n沖天香陣透長安<br />\n<br />\n滿城盡帶黃金甲"},{"pid":"940ae1bda90b6e81c48ccb528d8fe632f31bd363","tid":23364,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T01:53:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>老老豆豆 毛魔啲詩詞霸氣係噴晒出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n譬如？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n數天下英雄 還看今朝</blockquote><br />\n呢句你自己作？"},{"pid":"c494bf2cee8713d6dac9aece1d42bbccde9cd68f","tid":23364,"uid":46139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T01:53:23.000Z","msg":"满堂花醉三千客，一剑霜寒十四州。<br />\n<br />\n小學雞應該會覺得型"},{"pid":"1bb43e383c6ee9dd2062ba0f082ae80017f4d343","tid":23364,"uid":46139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T01:54:00.000Z","msg":"青门柳枝软无力，东风吹作黄金色。<br />\n<br />\n我覺得呢兩句好正"},{"pid":"e7b151bcca2786bd2a03654f243732bc7a5396bf","tid":23364,"uid":46139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T01:55:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>老老豆豆 毛魔啲詩詞霸氣係噴晒出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n譬如？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n數天下英雄 還看今朝</blockquote><